window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>An unstoppable army. A crumbling alliance. A final battle that will decide the fate of every Earth in existence.</b></p> <p>Colonel Vaughn Singleton and his multiverse-hopping team of soldiers, scientists, and smart-assed robots are out of time. The Necks—relentless, four-armed machines—have launched a devastating offensive across countless timelines. As humanity's last defenses falter, Vaughn's team races to reboot the timeline and stop the war before it begins.</p> <p>But when a mission deep behind enemy lines uncovers a buried truth about their robotic foes, everything changes. Faced with a revelation that upends their understanding of the war, Vaughn must choose between saving the enemy—or erasing them from existence.</p> <p>As alliances fracture and entire worlds burn, the team must risk everything in one final gambit. Because in the multiverse, there are no second chances… only infinite consequences.</p> <p>Infinitude <i>delivers a gut-punch of high-stakes action, mind-bending twists, and emotional payoff. Perfect for fans of The Expanse, Expeditionary Force, Live Die Repeat, and The Bobiverse, this explosive finale will leave you breathless.</i></p>"; 
